Responsibilities
Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree, any field.Required language(s): English, Bahasa IndonesiaAt least 10 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.Preferably CEO /GM / Director / Senior Managers specializing in Banking/Financial Services or equivalent.Full-Time position(s) available.Control all aspect in AR maintenance, manage team to achieve target.Review on weekly and monthly basis the results of collectability performance in all Bucket, and strengthen the controlling methodsMaximize Desk Collection functions to minimize customer past due, and maximize the Repossess success rate to reduce of the risk of Unit lost or being pawned or unofficial handing over unit to other.Maximizing and do the monthly review to make sure all Remedial and Collection Manager and Supervisor  already have a good control methods and shown the progress on monthly basis.Strong relationship or expanding network to Professionals Collectors / Police/ military to all over IndonesiaCoordination with Asset Management Unit in repossess and re-marketing Activities.Coordination with Legal Department, to ensure get fully back up support in order to avoid legal issue in terms of Repossession UnitReview weekly and Monthly Reports to always be alert on any possible miss calculation of plan that needs a change in strategReport to Operation Director for the performance of Collection KPI achievement.To create a SOP for Collection and Remedial activities.
